Day 7: Review and Introductory Codeforces Practice
Objective: Consolidate and apply to real problems.

Review (1-2 hours): Revisit all, rewrite 3 programs per day.
Practice (2-3 hours):
Codeforces: "Watermelon" (4A) – Approach: If w%2==0 && w>2 "YES".
"Theatre Square" (1A) – Approach: Ceil division for flags.
Solve 8 more 800-rated.

Analysis (30-45 minutes): Read editorials, journal.
